    "description": "<p>Kimbal is a fast-growing Indian energy-tech company pioneering smart energy solutions that modernize power distribution systems. We design and deliver advanced metering infrastructure (AMI) — including smart meters, communication networks, and cloud-based data platforms — to help utilities improve efficiency, accuracy, and grid reliability. Our products and solutions are deployed across multiple Indian states and supporting nationwide energy digitization initiatives with millions of smart meter installations. With a strong focus on innovation, scale, and quality, Kimbal empowers utilities and communities to build a smarter, more sustainable energy future.</p><p></p>",
